將三個 dataframe 合併為一
========================================================

方便後續處理

```{r}
# Now that we've verified they are all the same, we can combine them into a single data frame. 
krack_full_data_frame <- cbind(
  advice_data_frame, 
  friendship_data_frame$friendship_tie, 
  reports_to_data_frame$reports_to_tie
)
```



========================================================

